      <container name="回顾" eId="container_2">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold">回顾</span>其以往关于苏丹的决议，尤其是第<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1591(2005)">1591(2005)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1651(2005)">1651(2005)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1665(2006)">1665(2006)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1672(2006)">1672(2006)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1713(2006)">1713(2006)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1779(2007)">1779(2007)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1841(2008)">1841(2008)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1891(2009)">1891(2009)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1945(2010)">1945(2010)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/1982(2011)">1982(2011)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2035(2012)">2035(2012)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2091(2013)">2091(2013)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2138(2014)">2138(2014)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2200(2015)">2200(2015)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2265(2016)">2265(2016)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2340(2017)">2340(2017)</a>、<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2400(2018)">2400(2018)</a>和<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/RES/2455(2019)">2455(2019)</a>号决议，以及安理会2018年12月11日主席声明(<a href="https://undocs.org/ch/S/PRST/2018/19">S/PRST/2018/19</a>)，</p>
      </container>
      <container name="认定" eId="container_3">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold">认定</span>苏丹局势继续对该区域的国际和平与安全构成威胁，</p>
      </container>
      <container name="回顾" eId="container_4">
